== Running the tests

There are Cucumber and Rspec test for the Version Matrix application. The general philosphy is Cucumber tests for testing use cases, and rspec tests for the controller and model.

First you need to set-up the database. The following commands will get the development and test database schema set-up:
 - rake db:migrate
 - rake environment RAILS_ENV=test db:migrate

The Cucumber tests can be run with the following command:
 - bundle exec cucumber

The rspec unit tests can be run with the following command:
 - bundle exec rspec spec/
